comment: A 24 Second Shot Clock Violation is committed by the Heat.
Gasol (MEM) sets the screen on Dragic (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Whiteside (MIA) sets the screen on Randolph (MEM) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Gasol (MEM) dislodges Whiteside (MIA), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Randolph (MEM) makes incidental contact with Bosh (MIA) prior to the shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Conley's (MEM) drive and shot attempt.
Allen (MEM) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Bosh's (MIA) shot attempt.
Chalmers (MEM) dislodges Johnson (MIA) limiting his ability to rebound the ball.
Whiteside (MIA) makes contact with Gasol's (MEM) body that affects his shot attempt.
Bosh (MIA) sets the screen on Conley (MEM) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Chalmers (MEM) makes contact with Wade (MIA) as he secures the rebound.
Chalmers (MEM) maintains legal guarding position as a help defender and cleanly swipes the ball away from Wade (MIA)
Bosh (MIA) makes contact with Gasol's (MEM) arm that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Deng (MIA) commits a take foul on Lee (MEM).
Gasol (MEM) legally contests Deng's (MIA) shot attempt and cleanly blocks it.
Johnson (MIA) commits a take foul on Chalmers (MEM).
